Package marvel.model.character

Class CharacterInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • marvel.model.character.CharacterInfo
  • public class CharacterInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents data retrieved on a specific Marvel character from a previous InputModel search. Provides getters and setters for all fields.

    As all methods in this class are getters and setter, no further description is added for methods as usage is trivial.

    Fields description reference Marvel API's interactive documentation. See GET /v1/public/characters

    See Also:
    Comic, Event, ResourceUrl, Series, Story, Thumbnail
